{"version": 2, "width": 120, "height": 36, "title": "design-data — agent (MCP) (PLACEHOLDER)"}
[0.4, "o", "\u001b[1;33mPLACEHOLDER cast — re-record with ./record-casts.sh D\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.8, "o", "$ claude\r\n"]
[1.2, "o", "\u001b[1mClaude Code\u001b[0m — design-data MCP connected\r\n\r\n"]
[1.6, "o", "> Using the design-data MCP, look up the button component and tell me:\r\n"]
[1.8, "o", "  1. Its accessibility role and keyboard intents\r\n"]
[2.0, "o", "  2. Which states it declares\r\n"]
[2.2, "o", "  3. Which token resolves the default background color in dark mode\r\n"]
[2.4, "o", "  Show the answers with citations from the spec, not a guess.\r\n\r\n"]
[2.8, "m", "D1 prompt submitted"]
[3.0, "o", "\u001b[2m▶ calling mcp__design-data__component(component: \"button\")\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.6, "o", "\u001b[1mRole:\u001b[0m button (ARIA) · \u001b[1mKeyboard intents:\u001b[0m activate\r\n"]
[4.0, "o", "\u001b[1mStates:\u001b[0m hover, focus, disabled\r\n"]
[4.4, "o", "(Source: packages/design-data-spec/components/button.json)\r\n\r\n"]
[4.8, "m", "D2 role and states"]
[5.0, "o", "\u001b[2m▶ calling mcp__design-data__resolve(token: \"accent-background-color\", colorScheme: \"dark\")\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.6, "o", "\u001b[1mResolved:\u001b[0m #4069FD (rgb 64 105 253)\r\n"]
[5.8, "o", "(Source: packages/design-data/tokens · dark scheme · cascade winner)\r\n\r\n"]
[6.2, "m", "D3 dark-mode resolved value"]
[6.4, "o", "\u001b[2mAlternative:\u001b[0m same answers without a persistent MCP:\r\n"]
[6.6, "o", "  npx @adobe/design-data query --filter \"component=button\"\r\n"]
[6.8, "o", "  (agent skill — deterministic, low context cost)\r\n\r\n"]
[7.2, "m", "D4 agent skill alternative"]
[7.4, "o", "\r\n"]
